    "Accessibility and Scalability: Language models can be accessed through digital platforms, making them easily available to healthcare professionals regardless of their geographic location.",
    "This accessibility allows for widespread adoption and scalability, potentially benefiting a larger number of patients. 4.",
    "Continuous Learning: Language models can be continuously trained and updated with the latest medical information, ensuring that they stay current and incorporate the most recent advancements in the field of digital pathology.",
